{"id":9617,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/9617","type":2,"name":"星界の戦旗","name_cn":"星界的战旗","summary":"       星界系列中的《星界之战旗》 （星界の戦旗）\r\n　　亚布帝国究竟是怎样的一个社会呢？亚布人自称为星之眷族，不到绝对万不得已时，他们绝不让自己的双脚踏上行星的地面。他们的一辈子都在宇宙飞船上生活——要么是战舰上、要么就是商船上。亚布人不象普通人类那样繁衍，他们通过基因工程制造自己的后代，都具有蓝发美颜抗衰老的特性。他们的军队制服有点中国风的味道——或者说更象是满族式样，而他们的文字又象是古巴比仑的锲形字，亚布语发音生硬很象是德语或某种北欧语言。总之一切似曾相似却又是以崭新的方式谋求生存之国度。","eps":[{"id":54893,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54893","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"再会","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-04-14","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54894,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54894","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"幻炎作戦","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-04-21","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54895,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54895","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"突撃艦“バースロイル”","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-04-28","comment":5,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54896,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54896","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"初陣","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-05-05","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54897,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54897","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"華やかな狂気","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-05-12","comment":6,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54898,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54898","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"弔いの晩餐","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-05-19","comment":5,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54899,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54899","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"くらやみの逃亡","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-05-26","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54900,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54900","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"決戦前夜","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-06-02","comment":3,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54901,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54901","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"バースロイルの戦い","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-06-09","comment":3,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":54902,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/54902","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"流れる星","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2000-06-16","comment":5,"desc":"","status